title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-03-2013 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-03-2013 TUES






The Glenn Beck Program - 09/03/13 




The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET


Joe Pags fills in for Glenn Beck.
 Senator Ted Cruz calls in to talk with Joe.
 Buck Sexton also stops by to talk about the Syria debacle.

 Also, Dennis Michael Lynch talks about his new documentary,
            They Come to America part II.
